                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dragon exhales a pressurized jet of water that deals @Damage[9d6[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage] damage in an @Template[type:line|distance:80] (@Check[reflex|dc:26|basic|options:area-effect,forced-movement,inflicts:prone] save). Creatures that critically fail their Reflex save against the Hydraulic Breath are pushed back 10 feet and knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Prone]. The dragon can't use Hydraulic Breath again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Hydraulic Breath]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
